        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-md leading-relaxed">
          ¬øTienes una idea innovadora? Estoy aqu√≠ para escucharla y empezar a construir juntos.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8 pt-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6 group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-forest/20 flex items-center justify-center text-lime group-hover:bg-lime group-hover:text-deep-black transition-all">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
